---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Uses" description="Hardware, software, and tools I use day-to-day.">
  <main id="main" class="prose">
    <h1>What Gary Uses</h1>
    <p>Here's a non-exhaustive list of the hardware, software, and tools I use day-to-day.</p>
    <h2>Hardware</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Personal: M1 Max MacBook Pro</li>
      <li>Personal: Dell XPS Tower (dual boots Windows 11 Pro, Ubuntu 24.04)</li>
      <li>Work: M3 Pro MacBook Pro</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Software</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="https://code.visualstudio.com/">Visual Studio Code</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://iterm2.com/">iTerm2</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://obsidian.md/">Obsidian</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://1password.com/">1Password</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://maccheckbook.com/checkbookpro/index.html">Checkbook Pro</a></li>
    </ul>
    <h2>AI</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="https://anthropic.com/claude">Claude Code</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://openai.com/codex">Codex</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://cursor.com/product">Cursor</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://agentsview.io/">AgentsView</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://roborev.io/">RoboRev</a></li>
    </ul>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .prose {
    max-width: var(--reading-width);
  }
  .prose p {
    margin: var(--sp-4) 0;
  }
</style>
